---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service — EOB Decoder" description="Terms of Service for EOB Decoder. Understand your rights and responsibilities when using our tools.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F7B8C 0%, #2D4A7A 100%);" class="text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-bold mb-4 leading-tight" style="font-size: 40px;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-100" style="font-size: 16px;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-slate">

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Service Description</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">EOB Decoder is an AI-powered tool designed to help US patients understand their Explanation of Benefits (EOB) documents, identify potential billing errors, and generate dispute letter drafts. EOB Decoder is an independent software tool — it is not a law firm, a medical billing company, or a healthcare provider. Use of our tools does not constitute legal, medical, or financial advice.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">By using EOB Decoder, you agree to use our tools only for lawful purposes. You may use our tools for:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Personal, non-commercial review of your own medical bills and EOB documents</li>
        <li>Generating draft dispute letters for your own use</li>
        <li>Educational purposes to better understand medical billing</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-4">You may not use EOB Decoder to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-[#334155] leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>Generate fraudulent dispute letters or make false claims against insurers or healthcare providers</li>
        <li>Process medical information on behalf of others for commercial purposes without appropriate authorization</li>
        <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, scrape, or abuse our systems</li>
        <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">EOB Decoder's tools are powered by AI and are provided for informational purposes only. The explanations, error identifications, and dispute letter drafts generated by our tools are not guaranteed to be accurate, complete, or appropriate for your specific situation. You are solely responsible for reviewing and verifying any output before acting on it. EOB Decoder makes no representations or warranties about the outcome of any dispute you submit. Always consult a licensed healthcare advocate, insurance professional, or attorney for complex billing disputes.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">All content, design, and software on EOB Decoder is &copy; EOB Decoder 2026. You may not copy, reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without express written permission. The dispute letter drafts generated by our tools are provided for your personal use and may be freely modified and submitted by you.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">To the fullest extent permitted by law, EOB Decoder and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our tools or reliance on any output they generate. Our tools are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. We will indicate the date of the most recent update at the top of this page. Continued use of EOB Decoder after changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-[#1A2332] mt-10 mb-4" style="font-size: 22px;">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-[#334155] leading-relaxed mb-6">If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:amitsharma00261@gmail.com" class="text-[#0F7B8C] hover:underline">amitsharma00261@gmail.com</a></p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
